{"tid":1534820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無限期罷學到中大集會 而唔係番學校罷課","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:23:47.000Z","uid":30084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"109615fed81bff54c8cb3c7c9d0822f23b936444","tid":1534820,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"經過今日可見學校已經唔係一個安全既地方 <br />\n已經唔可以保證學校既人會做咩野去禁聲 <br />\n加上分散左各區既學校 想要支援都好難聚眾<br />\n<br />\n我建議 罷課既同學 應該全部到中大集會 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">人多先會安全</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外 罷課 唔係一兩日有用 我地需要既係長期抗爭<br />\n<br />\n請大家支持無限期罷課"},{"pid":"38d22f0a9dd37e797ac7858acd7bb5b87ba8fc0b","tid":1534820,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"次次都話知道好撚攰唔搞咁密 但每星期都keep住兩三劑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534726</a>"},{"pid":"ccda4eb42cda72eddb00e8538a3ecc9101e4c0b7","tid":1534820,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a948d58b5c1534bb520449954c16fe44eaafd4a","tid":1534820,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a7cae9674da2a6ad33a577191100220a5294e0b","tid":1534820,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac1365a55cb23683904c4a25bd4e0f7e2d100e51","tid":1534820,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"乜唔係轉哂去遮打咩"},{"pid":"1f770d45c703956d6e2024cd102b6b3f85d719fc","tid":1534820,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1365a55cb23683904c4a25bd4e0f7e2d100e51","tid":1534820,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"乜唔係轉哂去遮打咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"需要一個每日都可以去既集會地方 <br />\n無限期罷課"},{"pid":"13d0fc9871470f5a6e9bf521a6c24378062d03c8","tid":1534820,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"中大集會 無限期罷課"}]}